                            <comment id="15023213" author="tn" created="Mon, 23 Nov 2015 22:20:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report. It has been fixed in the following commits:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;3.6: fe23c9b04&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;4.0: 487ac1980&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The synchronization is now also on the coefficient list itself (which must be non-null), and thus there should be a slight performance improvement when creating different polynomials in multiple threads.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
